summary: Great adventure  ---  mysteries galore ! Two friends set out to find the truth behind the world, and discover the realities in a...
caption:
Great adventure  —  mysteries galore ! Two friends set out to find the truth behind the world, and discover the realities in a world where time is beside itself.

Teampeachyist ! will follow the thrilling tale of Pokemon Mystery Dungeon: Explorers Of Time, with a few twists & turns that deviate from the original story. It updates Bi-Weekly on Sundays.

Fall in love with these explorers as they choose between right & wrong  —  & you, the viewer, will have input ! send in asks, & help push the story along !

Adventure awaits !
